# Git LFS tracking
# NOTE: *.pkl LFS tracking has been REMOVED because:
# 1. Render (free tier) does not pull Git LFS objects during build/deploy.
# 2. The model *.pkl files are small enough to store directly in git.
# 3. LFS pointer files cause UnpicklingError at runtime on Render.
#
# IMPORTANT: You must also re-commit the actual binary files locally:
#   git lfs untrack '*.pkl'
#   git rm --cached models/*.pkl
#   git add models/*.pkl
#   git commit -m 'Remove LFS tracking from model files'
